video.title: We Bare Bears
video.synopsis: Grizzly, Panda and Ice Bear are three adopted bear brothers struggling against their animal instincts to fit into the civilized, modern human world.

episodes.synopsis: Grizz pitches his unfinished film, "Crowbar Jones: Origins," to Nom Nom, who isn't interested.
episodes.title: Crowbar Jones: Origins

episodes.synopsis: The bears go undercover to nab the thieves who replaced their favorite hot sauce with a stolen brand.
episodes.title: Hot Sauce

episodes.synopsis: The bears download the new Mom App to hire surrogate mothers but the results are disappointing.
episodes.title: Mom App

episodes.synopsis: Panda is devastated to learn that Lucy has a cool new boyfriend, and only advice from T-Pain can help.
episodes.title: The Limo

episodes.synopsis: Another online browsing session reveals videos that the brothers have posted to Everyone's Tube.
episodes.title: More Everyone's Tube

episodes.synopsis: Chloe asks the bears to help present her mind-reading invention to an absent-minded scientist.
episodes.title: Money Man

episodes.synopsis: Ranger Tabes learns of the existence of Charlie and helps the bears protect him from the Booby Trapper.
episodes.title: Rescue Ranger

episodes.synopsis: Charlie recalls his adventures in 1913 Mexico, befriending the outlaw El Oso and his gang.
episodes.title: El Oso

episodes.synopsis: Four more tales of Halloween include a zombie attack, a haunted house, a troll and a wishing machine.
episodes.title: Charlie's Halloween Thing 2

episodes.synopsis: A famous luchador tells his son the story of how the baby bears stepped in to wrestle for him.
episodes.title: Escandalosos

episodes.synopsis: The bears become famous when they lip sync for the broken animatronic band at Papa Bear's pizza joint.
episodes.title: Pizza Band

episodes.synopsis: The boys are adopted by an eccentric millionaire but soon discover they are playthings for his pet gorilla.
episodes.title: Adopted

episodes.synopsis: A very loud and rare bird keeps the bears awake with his deafening mating calls.
episodes.title: Wingmen

episodes.synopsis: Panda discovers his ugly new braces give him special electrical superpowers, which go to his head.
episodes.title: Braces

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears are working overnight on Christmas Eve at a video store when a thief pretending to be Santa breaks in.
episodes.title: Christmas Movies

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears make up an imaginary fourth friend named Silver Bear, whose heroics cause issues.
episodes.title: Imaginary Friend

episodes.synopsis: At the mall, the bears hang out for the day with their human counterparts, the Bros.
episodes.title: The Mall

episodes.synopsis: A sinkhole under Panda's bed leads to a network of tunnels dug by moles that worship his manga.
episodes.title: Tunnels

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears help a ramen chef perfect her recipes so that her father won't shut down her restaurant.
episodes.title: Ramen

episodes.synopsis: The bears head to the gym to see if they are "gym material." They are not.
episodes.title: The Gym

episodes.synopsis: A scary movie turns Panda into a germaphobe who now lives in a sealed bubble.
episodes.title: Bubble

episodes.synopsis: In the sewers of New York, the baby bears become disciples of the ninja master Cheddar.
episodes.title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears

episodes.synopsis: When he puts out a small picnic fire, Grizz is made an honorary fire marshall.
episodes.title: Fire!

episodes.synopsis: The bears take an immediate dislike to temporary new ranger Norm, who has a secret agenda.
episodes.title: Ranger Norm

episodes.synopsis: The bears become overreliant on a home assistance device and soon grow lazy and fat.
episodes.title: Shmorby

episodes.synopsis: Charlie finds some snake eggs and decides to adopt the hatchlings, who quickly tire him out.
episodes.title: Snake Babies

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears decide to build an elaborate sandcastle as their new home, but then must defend it.
episodes.title: Sandcastle

episodes.synopsis: The bears and the Bros become the stars of a reality television series, "Bros in the City."
episodes.title: Bros in the City

episodes.synopsis: At Chloe's family reunion, the bears fall victim to a series of sinister pranks by her cousin, Jon.
episodes.title: Cousin Jon

episodes.synopsis: Grizz, Ranger Tabes and the Poppy Rangers go camping on an island, but they forget to bring food.
episodes.title: Lord of the Poppies

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears find a mummy that must be returned to the museum by midnight to avoid a curse.
episodes.title: The Mummy's Curse

episodes.synopsis: Baby Ice Bear joins a trio of troublemakers in the seedy parts of London.
episodes.title: Band of Outsiders

episodes.synopsis: Tabes convinces Charlie to help her find the missing Kirk while the bears try to help some hikers.
episodes.title: Tabes & Charlie

episodes.synopsis: For Panda's birthday, Grizz and Ice take him to the hotel where the K-Pop band Monsta X is staying.
episodes.title: Panda's Birthday

episodes.synopsis: Stranded on a subway platform after missing their train, the bears must find some lost items while they wait.
episodes.title: Subway

episodes.synopsis: Grizz provides anger management therapy for Nom Nom, who must complete it to appear on a kids' TV show.
episodes.title: Anger Management

episodes.synopsis: Using an app, Panda makes a new friend named Tom who shares his interests, but Tom becomes too possessive.
episodes.title: Panda's Friend

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears are elated to find a one-hundred-dollar bill but can't figure out how they want to spend it.
Campers set up near the bears' cave and while Ice and Panda welcome them, Grizz becomes suspicious.
episodes.title: Neighbors

episodes.synopsis: The well-intentioned bears kidnap Chloe's mean professor when he refuses to discuss a bad grade with her.
episodes.title: Professor Lampwick

episodes.synopsis: Charles befriends a creature just like himself named Ralph but the bears don't like Ralph's cruel pranks.
episodes.title: Ralph

episodes.synopsis: An episode of a nature documentary films the bears going about their business, which includes grocery shopping.
episodes.title: Planet Bears

episodes.synopsis: When they discover that Ice Bear is a talented barista, the bears turn their cave into a popular coffee shop.
episodes.title: Coffee Cave

episodes.synopsis: Charlie hurts his foot helping the bears adjust their satellite dish, so they must sneak him into a hospital.
episodes.title: Charlie's Big Foot

episodes.synopsis: Chloe loses her favorite hoodie to the mean dog that lives next door, so she and Ice try to get it back.
episodes.title: The Demon

episodes.synopsis: An art dealer offers to buy Panda's portrait of Charlie, so Panda must get the painting back from him.
episodes.title: Panda's Art

episodes.synopsis: Ranger Tabes enlists Grizz to come along as an expert when she takes a group of girls on a cave expedition.
episodes.title: Poppy Rangers

episodes.synopsis: Ice and Panda help Lucy with deliveries while Panda minds her brother Clifford, who is prone to allergies.
episodes.title: Lucy's Brother

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to find new homes, the baby bears agree to become prizes in a popular carnival game of ball-toss.
episodes.title: The Fair

episodes.synopsis: With the local lake overcrowded, the bears are invited to Charlie's private lake but mistakenly publicize it.
episodes.title: Private Lake

episodes.synopsis: When Ranger Tabes' lunch is stolen, she launches a full-scale criminal investigation to find the culprit.
episodes.title: Lunch with Tabes

episodes.synopsis: Ice Bear drives the gang to see a meteor shower but the trip gets complicated when they pick up a hitchhiker.
episodes.title: Road Trip

episodes.synopsis: Panda encounters many obstacles, including a mad scientist, as he tries to return his dream girl's lost phone.
episodes.title: Summer Love

episodes.synopsis: The bears adopt a pet kitten and name it Thunderbolt but problems arise when they discover its true nature.
episodes.title: The Kitty

episodes.synopsis: Grizz shows his homemade movie to a focus group but notices that his audience is losing interest and leaving the screening.
episodes.title: Crowbar Jones

episodes.synopsis: Nom Nom is reunited with his long-lost brother Kyle but it turns out Kyle may not be everything he claims.
episodes.title: Kyle

episodes.synopsis: Ranger Tabes quits her job after breaking a deer's antler and the bears try to persuade her to return.
episodes.title: Citizen Tabes

episodes.synopsis: Panda agrees to be Lucy's dance partner for a big contest, but then discovers she's a terrible dancer.
episodes.title: Dance Lessons

episodes.synopsis: Ice Bear embarks on a mission to rescue his friend Yana, who has been kidnapped by the sinister Barry.
episodes.title: Icy Nights II

episodes.synopsis: Fleeing their roach-infested cave, the bears check into a dog hotel where Grizz is mistaken for a rabid pooch.
episodes.title: Dog Hotel

episodes.synopsis: To help Darrell raise enough money to save his mouse pad store, the bears become a "bear-stack" taxi.
episodes.title: Bear Lift

episodes.synopsis: Nom Nom's guests don't appear for the filming of his TV show so he enlists the bears as replacements.
episodes.title: The Nom Nom Show

episodes.synopsis: Angry that he was left out of playing a board game by Charlie and the bears, Ralph takes over their cave.
episodes.title: Ice Cave

episodes.synopsis: Grizzly makes the most of a day at the spa while Ice Bear plays ping pong and Panda takes a steam.
episodes.title: Spa Day

episodes.synopsis: Charlie tells spooky Halloween stories starring the bears, including one about haunted dolls and one about a "werebear."
episodes.title: Charlie's Halloween Thing

episodes.synopsis: Trekking to a chocolate festival, the bears help a burrow of bunnies living in fear of crows.
episodes.title: Bunnies

episodes.synopsis: Grizz agrees to help his pigeon friend Brenda and her pals, unaware they're plotting a jailbreak.
episodes.title: Pigeons

episodes.synopsis: Baby Panda lives carefree in a Chinese bear enclosure until a new stuffed-toy pal opens his eyes.
episodes.title: Panda 2

episodes.synopsis: Separated from his pals during a river-tubing trip, Panda must be rescued from a tribe of vegans.
episodes.title: Tubin'

episodes.synopsis: To win an ice cream sundae, the baby bears enter a laser tag game that becomes an all-out war.
episodes.title: Lazer Royale

episodes.synopsis: Grizz goes from cheerleader to player in a kickball showdown of Poppy Rangers vs. Ivy Rangers.
episodes.title: Ranger Games

episodes.synopsis: Grizz and Panda decorate Chloe's house while she and Ice Bear search for a perfect Christmas tree.
episodes.title: The Perfect Tree

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears disguise themselves as the father of Nate, a teenage singer entering a talent show.
episodes.title: Bearz II Men

episodes.synopsis: The bears battle a rival trio of roommates on a game show to determine who are the "best bros."
episodes.title: Bro Brawl

episodes.synopsis: When a hurricane hits, the bear brothers are separated from each other in different parts of town.
episodes.title: Hurricane Hal

episodes.synopsis: Stressed out by a sudden rise in popularity, Nom Nom visits a spa with his "comfort pet," Grizz.
episodes.title: Vacation

episodes.synopsis: The bears fall under the spell of bees that make delicious honey, so Ranger Tabes must rescue them.
episodes.title: Beehive

episodes.synopsis: In a day at the park, Ice Bear teaches martial arts, Grizz exercises and Panda sells his art.
episodes.title: The Park

episodes.synopsis: A head injury suddenly changes Ice Bear's personality into one that's cooler and more talkative.
episodes.title: I Am Ice Bear

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears come up with the "bear stack" during a game of basketball against a group of kids.
episodes.title: Baby Bears Can't Jump

episodes.synopsis: The bears go on a fishing trip led by a sea captain obsessed with catching a giant goldfish.
episodes.title: Go Fish

episodes.synopsis: At a school for the gifted, the baby bears alienate the other students by becoming teacher's pets.
episodes.title: Teacher's Pet

episodes.synopsis: Panda wins a contest and gets a private tour of Googs headquarters, but all is not as it seems.
episodes.title: Googs

episodes.synopsis: The baby bears compete with each other to score the one spot available delivering newspapers.
episodes.title: Paperboyz

episodes.synopsis: Ranger Tabes deputizes the bears so they can track down a fox that stole their belongings.
episodes.title: Bear Squad

episodes.synopsis: At the aquarium, the bears build a submarine to find the family of a baby squid they rescued.
episodes.title: Lil' Squid

episodes.synopsis: The bears discover a robot clone that Ice Bear had been building and turn it into their butler.
episodes.title: I, Butler

episodes.synopsis: While starring in a Canadian sitcom, Baby Grizz is threatened by the addition of a new cast member.
episodes.title: Family Troubles

episodes.synopsis: The bears have only a half hour to get the cake, rings and vows for Darrell's wedding to Sofia.
episodes.title: Best Bears
